Class RTStandardArguments

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.magicdgs.readtools.cmd.RTStandardArguments

  • public class RTStandardArguments
extends java.lang.Object
    Standard argument names for ReadTools. This encapsulates the names for all arguments that does not belong to legacy tools alone.
